{"title":"哀颂邓小平同志","authors":["莫文骅"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":2,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"哀颂邓小平同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫文骅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命低潮举义旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太行抗寇计出奇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南渡黄河穿敌腹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突破长江毁蒋基。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党内坎坷均屈委，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改革开放利群黎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一国两制英明策，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结安定众心齐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰功伟业铭青史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继承发展是无疑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今公已乘黄鹤去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安息勿虑亿民祈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九九七年二月廿日午夜于北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作者是曾参加过百色起义的红七军老战士。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}